{"tid":2092524,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利迷批評曼城列隊歡迎儀式不尊重","createTime":"2020-07-03T09:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T05:45:42.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"13896675b4e4062c872bfe845d18c64b8b3dd882","tid":2092524,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"利物浦贏得英超冠軍，按照傳統，其後比賽的所有對手於進場前，都要進行列隊歡迎儀式，曼城主場迎戰利物浦的比賽中當然也不例外，不過，事後卻有利物浦球迷批評對方的歡迎儀式不尊重。<br />\n<br />\n有利物浦球迷指出，在所有利物浦球員從球員通道進場之前，曼城的球員已經停止拍掌，而利物浦球員仍有球員未走完，就有主隊球員離開了隊列，認為曼城球員沒有尊重冠軍球隊，更有人直言這是見過最差的列隊歡迎儀式。"},{"pid":"efb1edb5f2b1bbf5323c931d3933f4a7dd2f6806","tid":2092524,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ac49c6876fad61c38e440aa6f0c7c5549556a8","tid":2092524,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287df87ef6bdaced49950e0a5600673de4067a86","tid":2092524,"uid":133100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:06:31.000Z","msg":"怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抵俾人4-0"},{"pid":"7ca95b5a8289e28a1a4f4072798262c49be30b1a","tid":2092524,"uid":157828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"喂 哥仔 尊重呀"}]}